text: Fredrik Wilhelm von Otter, born 11 April 1833, dead 9 March 1910, was a Swedish friherre, and naval officer, as well as a politician. He served as the Prime Minister of Sweden from 1900 to 1902. == References == Category:1833 births Category:1910 deaths Category:Admirals Category:Government ministers of Sweden Category:Prime ministers of Sweden Category:Swedish military people Category:Swedish nobility
